Package fr.ybo.csvengine.factory

Package containing all the object associate to the factory for write and read CSV File.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
CsvManagerFactory Factory which provide AbstractCsvReader and AbstractCsvWriter.
 

Class Summary
AbstractCsvReader Reader of CSV File.
AbstractCsvWriter Writer of CSV File.
DefaultCsvManagerFactory Default factory.
OpenCsvReader CsvReader based on OpenCsv.
OpenCsvWriter CsvWriter based on open-csv.
 

Package fr.ybo.csvengine.factory Description

Package containing all the object associate to the factory for write and read CSV File.
By default CsvEngine use open-csv, you can modify it :
You must implement the class CsvManagerFactory and pass it to CsvEngine with method CsvEngine.setFactory(CsvManagerFactory).

French : Package contenant l'ensemble des objets associés au mécanisme de factory pour l'écriture et la lecture de fichier CSV.
Par défaut le moteur utilise open-csv, il est touteois possible de modifier ce comportement.
Il suffit d'implémenter la classe CsvManagerFactory et de la fournit au moteur via la méthode CsvEngine.setFactory(CsvManagerFactory).
